data.title: TownTalk Magazine
data.meta_description: Lenexa's resident magazine with recreation program guide is published six times per year. It's mailed to each home and business in Lenexa.
data.text:
Lenexa's resident magazine and recreation program guide, TownTalk, is published six times per year and mailed to each home and business in Lenexa.

Current Issue (July 2024)

Read past issues

Not getting TownTalk?

Are you a Lenexa resident and business who isn't currently receiving the City's TownTalk magazine? If your address is being overlooked by mail carriers, complete this form, and we will add you to the list.
